\par \pard \s14\fi-360\li1080\sa43\tx1080 \{bmc smbull.bmp\}\tab Four suit stacks at the top of the playing area.
\par \pard\plain \s7\fi-360\li1080\sa180\tx1080 \f2\fs16 \{bmc smbull.bmp\}\tab Twelve stacks of four cards each in the playing area below.
\par \pard \s7\fi-360\li720\sa180\tx720 \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab The game begins with four Aces faceup in the suit stacks.
\par \pard \s7\fi-360\li720\sa180\tx720 \{bmc bull.bmp\}\tab You can move a card from the top of a stack to the corresponding suit stack if it is one higher in {\ul rank}{\v Rank} than the top card in the suit stack.  For example, 
